(72, 'ofsted-childcare-vouchers-tax-free-childcare-1', 'tennis-landing', 'Ofsted, Childcare vouchers & Tax-Free Childcare', '<p>As DRH Sports is an Ofsted registed organisation, we adhere to the highest standards of practice. From registers to data protection</p>', '#001642', 1, 2, '2020-11-18 15:56:51', '2020-12-05 17:34:08'),
(73, 'our-programmes-and-covid-19', 'tennis-landing', 'Our programmes and covid-19', '<p>We&#39;ve taken all precausions at DRH Sports to ensure that all players and caoches as safe as possible during the pandemic. We&#39;re committed to making sure that our venues are covid safe and our sessions are structured in the best way possible. To see our full covid guidance, please vist our <a href="http://demo.drhsports.co.uk/page/safeguarding-with-drh-sports">DRH Sports Covid page</a></p>', '#00afef', 1, 3, '2020-11-18 16:15:37', '2020-12-05 17:38:59'),
(74, 'our-courses-explained-1', 'course-listing/tennis?&cat=7', 'LSTC courses explained', '<p>Our DRH tennis coaching courses at Letchworth Sports &amp;&nbsp;Tennis Club run termly. The terms mirror the school terms with Spring, Summer and Autumn. Each course runs weekly with the exception of the half terms and school holidays.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe courses are split by age group and standard.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:20px;"><strong>AGE GROUPS:</strong></span><br />\r\n<strong>Mini Tots</strong> - Ages 3/4<br />\r\n<strong>Mini Red</strong> - Ages 5-8<br />\r\n<strong>Mini Orange</strong> - Ages 8/9<br />\r\n<strong>Mini Green</strong> - Ages 10<br />\r\n<strong>Junior </strong>- Ages 11-17<br />\r\n<strong>Adults</strong> for those ages 18+.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><span style="font-size:20px;"><strong>LEVELS:</strong></span><br />\r\n<strong>Club&nbsp;</strong>- Either new to tennis or still learning the basics. Not yet able to play matches.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Development&nbsp;</strong>- Can understand and perform all the basics in tennis and is of a level to start playing matches.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Team&nbsp;</strong>- Has experience in playing matches and also plays more than once per week. Ideally including 1to1 lessons.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Performance </strong>- The LSTC performance programme is by invite only and is for players competing regularly, training multiple times per week and having 1to1 lessons.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', '#001642', 1, 1, '2020-11-23 10:35:06', '2020-12-12 10:08:28'),
