g>Useful Contacts:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>For programme enquiries - </strong> please contact us at lstccoaching@drhsports.co.uk / 07901 903520<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>For website enquiries - </strong> contact info@drhsports.co.uk</span></p>', 'Player1', 110, '', '<p><strong>How to book this course: </strong><br />\r\n- Please select the person within your account that you wish to enrol on the course.<br />\r\n- If the persons name does not appear, please check their DOB is correct for this course.<br />\r\n- Only those people listed within your account with the correct DOB will show in the drop down list.&nbsp;- Only tennis club members can book this course. Please ensure that the participant is a member before attending the first session. You can register for tennis club membership by calling the reception team on 01462 675444</p>', 133, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 19, '2021-04-30', 1, '2020-12-12 03:33:29', '2020-12-17 16:49:23'),
(87, 'lstc-orange-development-3-sat-11am-12pm', '<p style="text-align: center;">This <strong>Green Club/Development</strong>&nbsp;coaching course is for children aged 10&nbsp;years old who are in the beginner stage of their tennis development.</p>', 'LSTC - Green Club/Dev - Sat 10-11am', 14, '156', 2, '165', 7, 'Beginner', '1607763588.png', '', 'Jan 9th, 16th, 23th, 30th. Feb 6th, 13th, 27th. Mar 6th, 13th, 20th, 27th.', 'Letchworth Sports & Tennis Club, Muddy Lane, Letchworth, SG6 3TB', 'Saturday 10-11am', '10 - 11', '8', '<p><strong>Term begins</strong>: Week commencing Jan&nbsp;4th and runs for 11 weeks<br />\r\n<strong>Session Dates:&nbsp;</strong>Jan 5th, 12th, 19th, 26th. Feb 2nd, 9th, 23rd. Mar 2nd, 19th, 16th, 23rd<br />\r\nThere will be no coaching during half term (Feb&nbsp;15th - 21st&nbsp;2021)&nbsp;<br />\r\n- You&nbsp;<strong><u>MUST&nbsp;</u></strong>be a member of LSTC to join this class. See joining info below.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In our&nbsp;<strong>Green&nbsp;club/Development</strong>&nbsp;groups&nbsp;we aim to teach our players the basics in a fun environment, with plenty of fun games to break up the learning.<br />\r\nThroughout a term we will cover the main four shots in tennis: forehand, backhand, serve and volley.<br />\r\nWe will mostly teach with basket feeding to enforce the players&#39; technique effectively but, as they progress, we will introduce rallying, which is a great way to get the players to work together to improve their tennis.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTo sign up for LSTC membership, please call the reception on 01462 675444</p>', '<p><span style="font-size:20px"><strong>Term Dates:</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px"><strong> </strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>Term begins - </strong>Monday January 4th 2021<br />\r\n<strong>Half Term - </strong>Monday February 15th - Sunday February 21st 2021<br />\r\n<strong>Term Ends - </strong>Sunday March 28th 2021</span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r