an></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><span style="font-size:20px"><strong>Useful Contacts:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>For programme enquiries - </strong> please contact us at lstccoaching@drhsports.co.uk / 07901 903520<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>For website enquiries - </strong> contact info@drhsports.co.uk</span></p>', 'Player1', 140.25, '', '<p><strong>How to book this course: </strong><br />\r\n- Please select the person within your account that you wish to enrol on the course.<br />\r\n- If the persons name does not appear, please check their DOB is correct for this course.<br />\r\n- Only those people listed within your account with the correct DOB will show in the drop down list.&nbsp;- Only tennis club members can book this course. Please ensure that the participant is a member before attending the first session. You can register for tennis club membership by calling the reception team on 01462 675444</p>', 133, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 28, '2021-04-30', 1, '2020-12-12 04:24:20', '2020-12-17 17:03:41'),
