(51, 'What does DRH Sports offer?', '<p>DRH Sports predominently offers tennis coaching classes and holiday kids camps. We also provide school clubs in various sports such as tennis, football, dodgeball, athletics, dance and multi-sports. Additionally we offer a service that allows tennis players and tennis coaches to connecct away from the tennis court to enhance the coaching experience.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 'user', 1, '2020-09-17 07:15:51', '2020-11-18 16:54:27'),
(52, 'What is Camp GO?', '<p>Camp GO is the name we have given to our holiday camps progrramme. Camp GO runs each schools holiday from multiple venues. Check out our <a href="http://demo.drhsports.co.uk/camp-listing">holiday camps page</a> for more information and how to book our kids camps.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 'user', 1, '2020-11-18 16:58:12', '2020-11-18 16:58:12'),
(53, 'Is DRH Sports Ofsted registered and can you accept childcare vouchers?', '<p>DRH Sports LTD is registered with Ofsted and therefore able to accept childrecare vouchers as payment. Please see the list below of the voucher providers that we are currently registered with. If the provider that you are registered with does not appear on the list below then please email us at info@drhsports.co.uk.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you&#39;d like to pay for a course or camp using childcare vouchers, all&nbsp;you need to do is book&nbsp;as normal and then select &#39;Use Childcare Vouchers&#39; as your payment method. If you have any problems paying with childcare vouchers using the information below please email us.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Computershare - 24767070</li>\r\n	<li>Mychildcaervouchers (Eden Red) - P21144641</li>\r\n	<li>Sodexo - 878811</li>\r\n	<li>Care4 - 05007023 - SG5 2JG</li>\r\n	<li>Busy Bees - EY562954</li>\r\n	<li>Fair Care - DRHS0219</li>\r\n	<li>Kiddivouchers - Search for DRH Sports Ltd</li>\r\n	<li>Co-op flexible benefits - 85118351</li>\r\n	<li>RG Childcare - 70858896419</li>\r\n	<li>For Fidelity - Please search for us using our Ofsted number EY562954 or our post code SG5 2JG</li>\r\n	<li>For Tax Free Childcare, please select Childcare vouchers as the payment option and then select Tax Free Childcare as the voucher provider. Once slected and the order confirmed you&#39;ll need to log into your Tax Free Childcare portal and add DRH Sports Ltd as a childcare provider. In order to add us, please search for us using some or all of the following information: 50031676316, EY number - EY562954, Company Name: DRH Sports Ltd, Activity address: MK10 9JQ</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, 0, 'user', 1, '2020-11-18 17:01:22', '2020-11-18 17:01:22'),
(54, 'What qualifications do the coaches hold?', '<p>We strive to ensure that our coaching team is the best it can be at all times. All our lead coaches are not only qualified in the sport that they are teaching, but also first aid trained, DBS (enhanced) checked, safeguard trained and hold public liability insurance.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, 'user', 1, '2020-11-18 17:11:29', '2020-11-18 17:11:29');
