(807, 0, 'ten_lan_act_heading', 'Our DRH Sports Pillars', 'tennis-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 07:31:29', '2020-11-13 06:10:37'),
(808, 0, 'ten_lan_act_sub_heading', 'Our mission at DRH Sports is not only to help all those in our programmes to become better at whichever sport they choose, but to also become better individuals. Our 5 pillars below set out the principles that we try to impart on all the players in our coaching programmes.', 'tennis-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 07:31:29', '2020-11-18 16:38:55'),
(809, 0, 'ten_lan_act1_image', '1606144972ten_lan_act1_image.png', 'tennis-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 07:31:29', '2020-11-23 09:52:52'),
(810, 0, 'ten_lan_act1_title', 'Teamwork', 'tennis-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 07:31:29', '2020-11-13 06:10:37'),
(811, 0, 'ten_lan_act1_description', '<p>Although tennis is predominantly an individual sport, it&#39;s important to promote teamwork as much as possible. We want players to feel part of something bigger than just themselves &amp; know that not only can it be gratifying to stand with your teammates, but it&#39;s also easier to work out problems when done together. <a href="http://demo.drhsports.co.uk/page/the-drh-pillars">Click Here to find out more</a></p>', 'tennis-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 07:31:29', '2020-12-05 04:28:23'),
(812, 0, 'ten_lan_act2_image', '1606144972ten_lan_act2_image.png', 'tennis-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 07:31:29', '2020-11-23 09:52:52'),
(813, 0, 'ten_lan_act2_title', 'Dedication', 'tennis-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 07:31:29', '2020-11-23 06:31:56'),
(814, 0, 'ten_lan_act2_description', '<p>In order to progress and suceed at anything in life, you must dedicate your time, effort and energy consistently. By doing this, no matter whether it&#39;s at tennis, another sport or at school/work, you&#39;ll improve and are more likely to suceed. Dedication is arguably the most important aspect of tennis development.&nbsp;<a href="http://demo.drhsports.co.uk/page/the-drh-pillars">Click Here to find out more</a></p>', 'tennis-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 07:31:29', '2020-12-05 04:28:23'),
(815, 0, 'ten_lan_act3_image', '1606144972ten_lan_act3_image.png', 'tennis-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 07:31:29', '2020-11-23 09:52:52'),
(816, 0, 'ten_lan_act3_title', 'Fairplay', 'tennis-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 07:31:29', '2020-11-13 06:10:37'),
(817, 0, 'ten_lan_act3_description', '<p>Fairplay is an absolute must within our DRH programmes. Whether it be with line calls, the score or a players on and off court, we strongly believe that all players should put fairplay at the forefront of their thoughts when playing the game.&nbsp;<a href="http://demo.drhsports.co.uk/page/the-drh-pillars">Click Here to find out more</a></p>', 'tennis-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 07:31:29', '2020-12-09 07:49:52'),
(818, 0, 'ten_lan_act4_image', '1606144972ten_lan_act4_image.png', 'tennis-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 07:31:29', '2020-11-23 09:52:52'),
(819, 0, 'ten_lan_act4_title', 'Respect', 'tennis-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 07:31:29', '2020-11-13 06:10:37'),
(820, 0, 'ten_lan_act4_description', '<p>Respect in tennis can come in many forms. Having respect for yourself, your opponents, your teammates, your coach and others who support you is key. We always want to promote players being humble on the court so having respect for yourself and others is an important ingredient in this process.&nbsp;<a href="http://demo.drhsports.co.uk/page/the-drh-pillars">Click Here to find out more</a></p>', 'tennis-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 07:31:29', '2020-12-05 04:28:23'),
(821, 0, 'ten_lan_act5_image', '1606144972ten_lan_act5_image.png', 'tennis-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 07:31:29', '2020-11-23 09:52:52'),
(822, 0, 'ten_lan_act5_title', 'Leadership', 'tennis-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 07:31:29', '2020-11-13 06:10:37'),
(823, 0, 'ten_lan_act5_description', '<p>Leadership is an important attribute for us at DRH Sports. Although not necessarily a quality you would normally associate to tennis, becoming a capable leader allows a player&rsquo;s confidence to grow alongside their ability to manage responsibilities.&nbsp;<a href="http://demo.drhsports.co.uk/page/the-drh-pillars">Click Here to find out more</a></p>', 'tennis-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 07:31:29', '2020-12-05 04:28:23'),
