(941, 0, 'foot_lan_act1_image', '1607520297foot_lan_act1_image.png', 'football-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 08:47:56', '2020-12-09 07:54:57'),
(942, 0, 'foot_lan_act1_title', 'Teamwork', 'football-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 08:47:56', '2020-12-09 07:49:56'),
(943, 0, 'foot_lan_act1_description', '<p>It&#39;s important to promote teamwork as much as possible. We want players to feel part of something bigger than just themselves &amp; know that not only can it be gratifying to stand with your teammates, but it&#39;s also easier to work out problems when done together. <a href="http://demo.drhsports.co.uk/page/the-drh-pillars">Click Here to find out more</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'football-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 08:47:56', '2020-12-09 07:49:56'),
(944, 0, 'foot_lan_act2_image', '1607520297foot_lan_act2_image.png', 'football-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 08:47:56', '2020-12-09 07:54:57'),
(945, 0, 'foot_lan_act2_title', 'Dedication', 'football-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 08:47:56', '2020-12-09 07:49:56'),
(946, 0, 'foot_lan_act2_description', '<p>In order to progress and suceed at anything in life, you must dedicate your time, effort and energy consistently. By doing this, no matter whether it&#39;s at tennis, another sport or at school/work, you&#39;ll improve and are more likely to suceed. Dedication is arguably the most important aspect of tennis development.&nbsp;<a href="http://demo.drhsports.co.uk/page/the-drh-pillars">Click Here to find out more</a></p>', 'football-landing', NULL, '2020-05-14 08:47:56', '2020-12-09 07:49:56'),
