(1120, 0, 'badges_desc', '<p><span style="font-size:20px;"><strong>Welcome to the DRH Tennis Pro - Badges</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On this page you can track the achievements of your players currently enrolled on DRH Sports tennis coaching programmes. Each badge represents a new skill that a player has achieved. It&#39;s designed to give parents an idea of their child&#39;s tennis playing level and progress before they are at the stage where they can compete in regular competitions. This is because once a player gets to a level where they are regularly competing, the matches they play become the measure of success, failure and progress.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some badges only last for a specific time before they will expire (generally this will be for a term). Each badge equates to a number of points for the player. The player&#39;s objective is to achieve as many points as they can within the coaching term. You can see a list and description of the achieved badges below. If you have any questions regarding the DRH Tennis Pro Badges feature, please email tennispro@drhsports.co.uk</p>', 'badges', NULL, '2020-06-29 01:41:24', '2020-11-20 05:49:28'),
