(1254, 0, 'stats_desc', '<p><span style="font-size:20px;"><strong>Welcome to the DRH Tennis Pro - Stats</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this feature a player in your account can see the statistics linked not only linked to the last match they uploaded, but also an average of the last <strong>5, 10, 15, 20</strong> and all matches. This serves as a powerful way to give great insight into the player&#39;s game and can be an active tool of their development. Additionally you also have the option to get a print out of the stats which can be shared with the players coach.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1) </strong>Select the player&#39;s name.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2) </strong>Select what you&#39;d like to see and click submit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want to find out more about how our Tennis Pro feature works, please <a href="http://demo.drhsports.co.uk/tennis-pro"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>click here</strong></span></a>. If you have any questions or issues regarding this feature, please do not hesitate to email us at tennispro@drhsports.co.uk</p>', 'badges', NULL, '2020-11-02 02:23:13', '2020-11-21 07:40:23'),
