(1344, 0, 'leaderboard_desc', '<p><span style="font-size:20px;"><strong>Welcome to the DRH Tennis Pro - Leaderboard</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This section is for mini tennis players enrolled in DRH tennis programmes and is also linked to the Badges section. Each of the badges acheived have points attached. The goal for each of the players is to achieve the highest number of points possible within a term.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1)</strong> Select the term you wish to view the points for.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2) </strong>Select the age group youd like to view. You may wish to just view the age group or your player or view all the age groups.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want to find out more about how our Tennis Pro feature works, please <a href="http://demo.drhsports.co.uk/tennis-pro"><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>click here</strong></span></a>. If you have any questions about the leaderboard of your players points, please email tennispro@drhsports.co.uk</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong>Please Note: </strong></span>The leaderboard is not an accurate measure of a players standard, ability or success. It&#39;s meant to act as a fun and engaging way for young players to be competitive and work hard to acheive their tennis goals.&nbsp;</p>', 'badges', NULL, '2020-11-20 03:56:09', '2020-11-21 07:40:23'),
